  keywords = {iron deficiency without anemia, ferritin, intravenous iron, fatigue, RCT, reference range},
  note    = {Double-blind RCT (n=90) of IV iron sucrose 800 mg vs placebo in premenopausal women, ferritin ≤50 ng/mL, normal Hgb. Primary benefit in subgroup with ferritin ≤15 ng/mL: fatigue decreased 1.8 vs 0.4 (p=0.005), 82\% vs 47\% improved (p=0.03). Standard labs flag deficiency only below 12 ng/mL.}
