  note    = {Prospective cohort analysis within WATTS study (n=552 on T4 monotherapy). DIO2 rs225014 CC genotype (16\% of population) associated with worse psychological wellbeing on T4 (p=0.03) and greater benefit from T4+T3 combination (p=0.03). Critically: NO impact on serum TSH, T3, or T4 levels. Establishes tissue-level T3 deficiency invisible to standard thyroid function testing.}
